name: Be Bold
description:
Print Image Width: 29 cms / 11.4 in
Print Image Height: 39 cm / 15.4 in

Printed on 200gsm fine art card, using inks that will not fade. 

The high quality bright white smooth matt card used ensures a sharp and intense image that has very rich and vibrant colour. 

Fits perfectly into Ikea 'Ribba' frames with mount. 

This print will be mailed to you protected in a sturdy mailer tube (A3) or Mailer envelope (A4).

This work can be personalized for you through color and text, please message me with request.


Prints also available in the following size:

A4 
Print Image Height: 29 cms / 11.4 in
Print Image Width: 20cms / 7.9 in


Framing is also available, with free delivery within Australia- Email me for details

Thank you for visiting my shop.
